# Georgia Legislative Navigator

A tool to track legislation and meet those in power at the Georgia General
Assembly.

## Contributing

This project requires the following tools to be installed on your system:

- Node.js (http://nodejs.org)
- Grunt.js (http://gruntjs.com)

After installing those tools, run the following command to install the Node.js
modules required for development:

    $ npm install

### Building the Project

Before deploying, the code in this project is optimized for network delivery.
To build the project, run the following command:

    $ grunt build
